### Location

Located on the east side of Ranch Road 620 between the traffic lights at Clara Van and Kollmeyer Drive.  Directly across from the entrance of the Lexus dealership and Sandeez Hamburgers.  

### Sale

 80 feet of Ranch Road North 620 Frontage in exploding Lakeway business district.   Warehouse/office is a single story building constructed of steel and rock façade located in an area that is projected to double in size in the next 10 years.  Building is approximately 2484 sqft (buyer must verify) on 0.2883 acres located in Lakeway directly across 620 from the Lexus dealership entrance, and contains a metal roll up door and a stone monument sign, that is adjacent to the highway.  Property is currently leased with approximately 2 years remaining.  Lease is triple net and is competitive with market and contains escalations.  HVAC is tenant controlled.  A great property in a prime location with huge potential.   It won't last long.   

*Seller will consider owner financing with qualified buyer.*

**Lot may be combined with 103 Ranch Road 620 S, Lot 28 for purchase of both buildings as a single package purchase. **

Waiting on site plan approval and hoping to break ground in April of 2017.  The expected delivery for the shell buildings is the end of Q3 2017.  The project is configured into three separate office buildings and will be approximately 70,000 square feet in total.  This entire project is 1:200 parking so it has the ability to go all medical.  The configuration of the property is below.  

Building One (Front Building) is a “Class A” MOB 
•	45,000 square feet of rentable square footage
•	Typical Elements of Class A construction with multiple elevators, storefront glass windows, steel structure, common area bathrooms, large atrium and covered parking 
•	Prominent location at the corner of Manchaca and Dittmar/Davis
•	Expected Leasing Rates of $26NNN-$28NNN year one rate with TI allowance of $40 per sqft.
•	Expected Offering Price of $245 per square foot for warm shell, with all common area elements; entries, elevators, halls, bathrooms, etc. in place


Building Two (second building from the corner) is a “Class A- suburban MOB”
•	12,000 square feet 
•	100% masonry veneers, wood construction, stone/stucco exterior, elevator 
•	Expected lease rates of between $22NNN-$24NNN year one rate with TI allowance of $40 per sqft
•	Expected sales rate of + $200 for cold dark shell

Building Three (third building from the Corner) is a “Class A- suburban MOB”
•	12,000 square feet 
•	100% masonry veneers, wood construction, stone/stucco exterior, elevator 
•	Expected lease rates of between $22NNN-$24NNN year one rate with TI allowance of $40 per sqft
•	Expected sales rate of + $190 for cold dark shell

Can deliver in shell condition, white-box or turnkey.

### Location

This location is settled nicely in the middle of North Austin directly off of Hwy 183. Surrounded by numerous residential neighborhoods and apartments, department stores, schools, and local tourist spots. Nested near  Lamar Blvd., Anderson Lane, and Hwy 183,  this location is a premium in North Austin. 

### Lease description

This space is great for a retail opportunity seeking tremendous signage, location, and traffic count or an office looking for easy access from Lamar and Hwy 183. The area is one of the busiest in Austin and will provide rare exposure.

Lease Only. Great location off Bandera Rd. Well maintained office + warehouse space available. Approx 795sf of office space currently consists of 3 rooms + 1/2 bath. Office space has access to approx 282sf garage/warehouse with 10' x 10' overhead door. Rent includes water + sewer, tenant pays all other utilities. 3 parking spaces in front of office.

Property For Lease

1,540 & 3,080 Sq Ft. new modern office/warehouse suites 

Modern designed flex suites

Built for small business by small business.  Building 1 is now full.  We are leasing building 2, which is under construction and is due to be completed in mid-August. 
 Designed by the brilliant contemporary architect Tom Hurt and brought to you by Jack Trade Properties with Three main goals in mind:  

1. Efficiency - We sought to create space that was highly efficient in not only its use of materials and on-going consumption of energy, but perhaps more importantly, space. Every square foot of each unit has been considered in an effort to deliver the most effective use of space possible. This means that each space can consume less of energy, building materials, and overall footprint, which lower rent and operating cost for you.

  2. Design - With modern minimalism in mind and a clean elegant inspiration we crafted a home for your business that you can be proud of and appeal to the current generation of consumer and workforce. 

  3. Effective functionality - By this, we not only mean to create space that properly fits your tools and products of your trade, we also mean that it fits a new generation of people. Every space had ample natural lighting, a full kitchen, aesthetically appealing outdoor spaces, and what we call a lady-friendly bathroom facility where a urinal is provided for the men.   All suites are pre-finished and with two sizes 1,540 Sq Ft and 3,080 Sq Ft. 

 Located just over the border from Austin in Pflugerville and 1 mile from I-35.
